reviewText: was not what I expected, it was 2 dudes with a clipboard sitting talking about each member of the Freebirds,  very little clips of matches, maybe only at 5 second pieces. sound quality was terrible.  I hate this so bad I might throw it away and never take the risk of buying another vintage wrestling video.
I would rather listen to Michael Hayes tell the history of The Freebirds.
